CWEs: CWE-129: Improper Validation of Array Index
description: The function is vulnerable to null pointer dereference because it does not check if the objects it is calling methods on (yy, $$) are null or undefined. It is also vulnerable to improper validation of array index because it does not check if the array index it is accessing is within the bounds of the array. Lastly, it is vulnerable to incorrect calculation because it does not check if the values it is performing arithmetic operations on are numbers.
